-- ('{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"7b3rp\",\"text\":\"Last night, I had the happiest dream. In it, I was walking through a beautiful garden filled with all kinds of flowers. The sun was shining, and there was a gentle breeze blowing through the air.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"1589s\",\"text\":\"As I wandered through the garden, I came across a group of my closest friends. We all hugged and laughed and talked about how grateful we were to have each other in our lives.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"54r1v\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"4ojjf\",\"text\":\"After a while, we sat down on a patch of soft grass and enjoyed a picnic together. We ate delicious food and drank sweet lemonade, and the conversation flowed effortlessly between us.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"55de8\",\"text\":\"As the sun started to set, we all stood up and held hands in a circle. We closed our eyes and took a deep breath, feeling grateful for the love and joy that surrounded us.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"2hg3l\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"al94v\",\"text\":\"When I woke up, I felt a warm, happy glow in my heart. Even though it was just a dream, it reminded me of how lucky I am to have such wonderful people in my life.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}', 3),

-- ('{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"6m6lq\",\"text\":\"Today was a productive day of coding. I spent several hours working on a new feature for an app I''m building, and I''m pleased with how it''s coming along.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"dra1\",\"text\":\"The feature involves creating a pop-up window that displays some additional information when the user clicks on a specific button. I had to do some research on how to create pop-up windows in JavaScript, but once I figured it out, the code came together pretty easily.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"65p6n\",\"text\":\"Here''s a snippet of the code I wrote:\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"9vrc7\",\"text\":\"javascriptCopy code// Define the function to create the pop-up window\nfunction createPopup() {\n  // Create a new window object\n  let popup = window.open(\\"\\", \\"Popup\\", \\"width=300,height=200\\");\n  \n  // Add some content to the pop-up window\n  popup.document.write(\\"<p>Here''s some additional information!</p>\\");\n}\n\n// Call the function when the user clicks on the button\ndocument.querySelector(\\"#myButton\\").addEventListener(\\"click\\", createPopup);\",\"type\":\"code-block\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":19,\"length\":422,\"style\":\"CODE\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"21het\",\"text\":\"This code defines a function called createPopup that creates a new pop-up window when called. The window is given a width and height of 300 and 200 pixels, respectively, and some content is added to it using the document.write method.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":36,\"length\":11,\"style\":\"CODE\"},{\"offset\":212,\"length\":14,\"style\":\"CODE\"},{\"offset\":36,\"length\":11,\"style\":\"BOLD\"},{\"offset\":212,\"length\":14,\"style\":\"BOLD\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"8feeq\",\"text\":\"The function is then attached to a button on the page using an event listener. When the button is clicked, the createPopup function is called, and the pop-up window appears.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":111,\"length\":11,\"style\":\"CODE\"},{\"offset\":111,\"length\":11,\"style\":\"BOLD\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"c3fmm\",\"text\":\"It''s always satisfying when a piece of code comes together smoothly like this. I''m looking forward to continuing to build out this feature and seeing it in action!\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}', 4),

-- ('{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"bnvch\",\"text\":\"Dear Joey,\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"bh437\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"djrab\",\"text\":\"I''ve been carrying a lot of anger and hurt towards you for a long time now, and I think it''s time for me to let it go. I know that holding onto this resentment isn''t serving me or you in any way, and I want to work towards forgiveness.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"43bhi\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"1t4tu\",\"text\":\"I want to start by acknowledging that I''ve played a role in the breakdown of our relationship. I know that I''ve said and done things that have hurt you, and for that, I''m truly sorry. I also recognize that you''ve probably said and done things that have hurt me, and I want you to know that I''m willing to forgive you for those things.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"4f51a\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"c28s0\",\"text\":\"I want to believe that you''re capable of growth and change, just as I am. I want to believe that we can move past our past hurts and build a new, healthier relationship. But in order for that to happen, I need to let go of my anger and resentment towards you.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"f8ahg\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"7an7f\",\"text\":\"So I''m writing this letter as a first step towards forgiveness. I''m not saying that everything is automatically okay between us, but I am saying that I''m willing to work towards a new beginning.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"910ku\",\"text\":\"I hope that you can find it in your heart to forgive me for the pain I''ve caused you, and I hope that we can move forward together in a spirit of love and understanding.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"c85jg\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}', 6),


-- ('{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"f88pj\",\"text\":\"Through a long and painful process, I''ve learned that happiness is an insid
-- e job - not based on anything or anyone in the outer material world. I''ve become a different and better person - not perfect, but still a work in progress.\",\"type\":\"blockquote\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"3h8qm\",\"text\":\"Alana Stewart\",\"type\":\"blockquote\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[{\"offset\":0,\"length\":13,\"key\":0}],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"28g1l\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"1t3od\",\"text\":\"I read a quote today that really resonated with me. Alana Stewart said, \\"Through a long and painful process, I''ve learned that happiness is an inside job - not based on anything or anyone in the outer material world. I''ve become a different and better person - not perfect, but still a work in progress.\\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"7dq7\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"cpkki\",\"text\":\"This quote really hit home for me because I''ve been struggling with finding happiness lately. I''ve been looking for it in all the wrong places - in my job, my relationships, my possessions - and I''ve come up empty-handed every time.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"bvoac\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"tpmi\",\"text\":\"But reading this quote made me realize that happiness isn''t something that can be found outside of myself. It''s something that comes from within, from being at peace with myself and the world around me.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"5m8gs\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"a2tsi\",\"text\":\"I''m not saying that I''ve suddenly found the secret to happiness, but I''m starting to see that the journey towards it starts with me. I need to work on becoming a better person, not for anyone else''s sake, but for my own.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"3ar1b\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"aljbo\",\"text\":\"I''m grateful for this reminder that I have the power to create my own happiness, and that it''s never too late to start making changes for the better.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{\"0\":{\"type\":\"LINK\",\"mutability\":\"MUTABLE\",\"data\":{\"href\":\"https://www.brainyquote.com/authors/alana-stewart-quotes\",\"url\":\"https://www.brainyquote.com/authors/alana-stewart-quotes\"}}}}', 8),



-- ('{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"68vr7\",\"text\":\"Today, I took a few minutes to think about some happy memories from my past, and one that came to mind was from a summer day a few years ago.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"8n066\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"f3q1o\",\"text\":\"I was sitting outside with my closest friends, laughing and chatting as we enjoyed the warmth of the sun on our skin. We had a picnic spread out in front of us, and we all shared stories about our lives and the adventures we had been on.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"ct23e\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"7b1hb\",\"text\":\"There was something so special about that moment, something that I can''t quite put into words. It was just one of those times where everything felt right in the world, and I was filled with a sense of joy and contentment.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"e75fa\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"af8fg\",\"text\":\"Thinking back on that day made me feel grateful for the people in my life who bring me happiness, and it reminded me to take the time to appreciate the small, beautiful moments that make life so special.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}', 9),


